quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,Alif Laam Miim
  32,2,Ihishurwa ry’igitabo kidashidikanywaho (Qur’an) ryaturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose
  32,3,"Cyangwa bavuga ko (Muhamadi) ari we wayihimbye? (Si ko bimeze), ahubwo yo ni ukuri kwaturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe ngo uyifashishe mu kuburira abantu batagezweho n’umuburizi uwo ari we wese mbere yawe kugira ngo bayoboke"
  32,4,"Allah ni We waremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma aganza hejuru ya Ar’shi. Nta wundi murinzi cyangwa umuvugizi muzagira utari We. Ese ntabwo mwibuka"
  32,5,"Ayoborera mu kirere gahunda zose (z’ibiremwa) zigana ku isi, maze zikazamuka zigana iwe mu munsi umwe ungana n’imyaka igihumbi mu yo mubara (ku isi)"
  32,6,"Uwo (Allah) ni Umumenyi w’ibyihishe n’ibigaragara, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  32,7,"We watunganyije buri kintu yaremye, akanatangira iremwa ry’umuntu utari uriho, amuremye mu ibumba"
  32,8,Hanyuma agena ko kororoka kwa muntu bizabaho binyuze mu mazi aciriritse (intanga)
  32,9,"Maze aramutunganya, amuhuhamo roho imuturutseho; abaha ukumva, amaso n’umutima. Ariko ni gake (yemwe bantu) mushimira"
  32,10,"Baranavuga bati “Ese (nidupfa) tukaburira mu gitaka, tuzasubizwa ubuzima bundi bushya?” Ahubwo bo bahakana kuzahura na Nyagasani wabo"
  32,11,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Malayika w’urupfu ubashinzwe azabatwara ubuzima; hanyuma kwa Nyagasani wanyu ni ho muzasubizwa.”